\": \"raymond91125\"\n60:       },\n61:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n62:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please create a new term vesicle membrane tethering activity. In addition to PMID:19887069 that focuses on ER-Golgi membrane traffic, include a general article that also covers synaptic vesicle transport and targeting.\",\n63:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T23:34:07Z\",\n64:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n65:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n66:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n67:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n68:         {\n69:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n70:           \"users\": {\n71:             \"totalCount\": 1\n72:           }\n73:         }\n74:       ],\n75:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863#issuecomment-4240276968\",\n76:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n77:     },\n78:     {\n79:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws78vYUl\",\n80:       \"author\": {\n81:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n82:       },\n83:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n84:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/24372402903)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n85:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T23:34:34Z\",\n86:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n87:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n88:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n89:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n90:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863#issuecomment-4240278821\",\n91:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n92:     },\n93:     {\n94:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws78vmB1\",\n95:       \"author\": {\n96:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n97:       },\n98:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n99:       \"body\": \"Created new term **vesicle membrane tethering activity** (GO:7770062) as a child of [GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/QuickGO/term/GO:0140177).\\n\\n**Definition:** A membrane-membrane adaptor activity that provides the first point of contact and physically bridges the vesicle membrane and its target membrane prior to vesicle docking and fusion.\\n\\n**References:**\\n- `PMID:19887069` — Sztul & Lupashin 2009, *FEBS Lett*, \\\"Role of vesicle tethering factors in the ER-Golgi membrane traffic\\\" (as requested)\\n- `PMID:19575650` — Yu & Hughson 2010, *Annu Rev Cell Dev Biol*, \\\"Tethering factors as organizers of intracellular vesicular traffic\\\" — a broad review covering tethering factors across intracellular trafficking pathways, including the plasma-membrane exocyst and CATCHR-family complexes (Munc13 has a CATCHR/MUN-domain fold and is a key synaptic vesicle tethering factor)\\n\\nA note on the second reference: you asked for an article that \\\"also covers synaptic vesicle transport and targeting.\\\" Yu & Hughson 2010 is a general review that includes synaptic-relevant tethers (exocyst, CATCHR/Munc13) within its broader scope. If you'd prefer a more synapse-focused companion reference, I'd suggest `PMID:23164531` (Hallermann & Silver 2013, *Trends Neurosci*, \\\"Sustaining rapid vesicular release at active zones: potential roles for vesicle tethering\\\") or `PMID:22794257` (Südhof 2012, *Neuron*, \\\"The presynaptic active zone\\\"). Happy to swap or add — just let me know.\\n\\nSynonyms added:\\n- `vesicle membrane tether activity` (EXACT)\\n- `vesicle tethering activity` (EXACT)\\n\\nPR: geneontology/go-ontology#31895\\n\\n---\\n🤖 **Generated by @dragon-ai-agent**\\n- Model: `claude-opus-4-6`\\n- Agent harness: claude-code\\n- Triggered by: @raymond91125\\n- Run: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/24372402903)\",\n100:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T23:49:27Z\",\n101:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n102:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n103:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n104:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n105:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontolo